# Keeps the indexer's Docker build context lean — see render.yaml's
# nebulous-world-indexer service, dockerContext: . (repo root, needed
# because indexer/Cargo.toml is now a member of the root Cargo workspace,
# see /Cargo.toml). indexer/Dockerfile only COPYs Cargo.toml, Cargo.lock,
# programs/nebulous_world, indexer/{Cargo.toml,src,decoder,migrations,
# dlmm-bridge} — everything below would just bloat the build upload with
# no benefit, or (worse) leak local secrets/dev artifacts into an image
# layer.
.git
.worktrees
node_modules
**/target
.next
.anchor
.surfpool
app
docs-site
indexer/dlmm-bridge/node_modules
indexer/dlmm-bridge/dist
.env
.env.*
*.log
.DS_Store
